2. **[GrantAccessModal.tsx](file:///c:/Users/extra/OneDrive/Desktop/WMS-AE/WarehouseManagementSystem/src/auth/components/GrantAccessModal.tsx)**: Change `onSave` handler to upsert into `user_permissions` table via Supabase client
3. **[App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/extra/OneDrive/Desktop/WMS-AE/WarehouseManagementSystem/src/App.tsx)**: Load permissions from DB on login, cache in state, remove localStorage read

